== cc65 on GNU/Linux ==

You have two options to install cc65:

* You can download pre-built packages for RPM based systems (OpenSUSE) and for DEB based systems (Debian) from [http://software.opensuse.org/download.html?project=home%3Astrik&package=cc65].

* You can just proceed as described in [http://oliverschmidt.github.io/cc65/getting-started.html Getting Started].